1.1.name: wordpress/eu-cookiewet-plugin
1.1.description: A simple WordPress plugin which helps you comply with the EU cookies and privacy directive by showing a message that cookies are used on the website. The plugin shows a bar at the top of the page where website visitors are told that the site uses cookies. The plugin will also create a page within WordPress where you can place your cookie policy.
